Title: You've Got Male
Plot: Grissom and Sara are called to the crime scene when two murder victims are found hidden in pipes at a construction site in the middle of an alfalfa field, while Catherine and Nick investigate an ostensible hunting accident.
GuestStars: Amanda Wyss, Holly Fulger, Clayton Rohner, Rodney Rowland, Kirk B.R. Woller, Simon Brooke, Amanda Righetti, Todd Sandler, Edmund Wyson, Robia LaMorte, Thomas Kopache, Nick Chinlund
